// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1394 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: a09e9900-6af3-54a0-b071-14cc87238311

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
